From 021bd059b68e9fa12d49061a777eeed545dfb218 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Nicolas Velasquez <nicolas.velasquez1233@gmail.com>
Date: Sat, 18 Apr 2026 05:45:55 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] feat(phase1): security headers, MDC correlation, global 404
 handler

- SecurityConfig: add X-Content-Type-Options, X-Frame-Options DENY,
  HSTS (1yr + subdomains), Cache-Control, Content-Security-Policy via
  StaticHeadersWriter
- RequestIdFilter: wire requestId into MDC on every request so all
  log lines carry requestId automatically; cleanup in finally block
- GlobalExceptionHandler: consistent ProblemDetail for 404
  (NoHandlerFoundException + NoResourceFoundException), 400 validation
  errors with field-level error list, and generic 500 fallback
- application.properties: enable throw-exception-if-no-handler-found
  and disable default resource mappings so 404 reaches the handler
- Tests:
  SecurityHeadersIntegrationTest - verifies 5 headers on 200 and 401
  GlobalExceptionHandlerIntegrationTest - verifies 404 returns JSON
    ProblemDetail with status/title/path fields
  AuditLoggingIntegrationTest - extended with requestId-in-meta and
    method/status assertions (Testcontainers, RUN_TC=true)
